title: Bresha Webb Interview and more
itunes:title: Bresha Webb Interview and more
description:
Wednesday 8/22 - Today on the show we had actress Bresha Webb stop by, or really should say Tiny Harris, because her impersonation of Tiny you wouldn't be able to tell the difference. Also. Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Dr. Scott Baker for wrongly removing a kidney during a botched procedure and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee", with one listener having his insecurities catching up to him after giving his girlfriend a hall pass.
